dieser Fragen auf interdisziplinäre Weise nach. Antworten geben u.a. der Philosoph Peter Sloderdijk, der Theologe Johannes Hoff, der Genetiker Markus Hengstschäger, die iranische Künstlerin Shirin Neshat, der Neurobiologe Joachim Bauer, der Soziologe Hartmut Rosa oder die Regisseurin Jacqueline Kornmüller.  aWe are all too familiar with the complex new triggers of geopolitical uncertainty: a financial system that knows no boundaries, renationalization, desecularization, and both the bright and dark sides of technological revolutions. Yet the big picture often eludes us. GlobArt-Academy 2014 is devoted to addressing these issues.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aGlobalizationxForecastingvCongresses. 0aInvisibilityxSocial aspectsvCongresses. 0aSocial changexForecastingvCongresses. 0aUncertaintyxForecastingvCongresses. 4aArbeit. 4aBildung. 4aEhtik. 4aFilm. 4aKunst. 4aMensch-Maschine. 4aPhilosophie. 4aSoziologie. 4aTechnik. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh1 aBauer, Joachim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChobot, Dagmar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGlobArt, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHabison, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHoff, Johannes, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKerbler, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKessler, Claudia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLloyd, John, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNeshat, Shirin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRosa, Hartmut, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/voc